					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">nineTENdo wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Is that why when ever you have a graphic in the $00 tile and you load a name tables it comes up on the whole screen on every tile.  How do you avoid this?</div>
<br />By filling the nametable with a tile other than $00. For instance, <em>Super Mario Bros.</em> has a 0 digit glyph in $00 but a space in $24, and it fills the nametable (except the attributes) with $24.</div>

